  <brief_title>Mitral Valve Reconstruction in Chronic Heart Failure (CHF): Identification of Predictors for a Successful Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Mitral Valve Reconstruction in Patients With Chronic Heart Failure and Secondary Mitral Insufficiency: Identification of Predictors for a Successful Therapy</official_title>
