  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Age &gt; 18 years old

          2. Dilatative Cardiomyopathy with LVEF &lt; 35%

          3. NYHA III oder IV under maximal medical treatment

          4. Angiographic and hemodynamic MI &gt; II° (LAP- mean pressure &gt; 15-20 mmHg; LA v-wave-oder
             PCWP v-wave &gt; 35 mmHg under exercise)

          5. Echocardiographic MI &gt; II°

          6. At least 1 hospitalization for heart failure before OP

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Secondary Cardiomyopathy by vitium cordis

          2. Planned secondary procedure like CABG, aortic valve surgery, surgery of the tricuspid
             valve etc

          3. Inclusion in another trial

          4. Euro-Score &gt; 30%

          5. Former valve operation or CABG
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
